data.chText: 磁带盒；盒式磁带； 卡式磁带
data.enText: a small flat plastic case containing tape for playing or recording music or sound

data.chText: 盒式磁带录音机 / 放音机

data.enText: a video cassette (= for recording sound and pictures)
a plastic case containing film that can be put into a camera

tr: a container that holds a magnetic tape used for recording or playing sound or video

value.def: A cassette is a small, flat, rectangular plastic case containing magnetic tape which is used for recording and playing back sound or film.

example.ex: His two albums released on cassette have sold more than 10 million copies.
example.tran: 他的两张专辑的磁带销量突破了1,000万。

value.def: A cassette is the container or case for the film that you load into a camera.
